    <div class="pgm-ap-faq__list">

      {%- assign faqs = "Do I need any equipment?|Do I need any equipment?,It Doesn't Require Equipment|No. Every exercise in the program is designed to be done at home using only your body and a floor. Some exercises use a wall, a chair, or a block — items you already have.;I've had surgery or have a serious condition. Is this safe for me?|Safe for Most Conditions|The Egoscue Method is non-impact and non-manipulative. It has been used safely by people recovering from surgery and managing chronic conditions. However, you should consult your physician before starting any new exercise program.;How is this different from yoga, stretching, or physical therapy?|It's Different|Yoga and stretching address flexibility and mobility, but they don't systematically correct structural misalignment. Physical therapy typically targets a specific injury site. The Egoscue Method maps your entire postural system and corrects the root cause — not just the symptom.;How quickly will I see results?|Results Timeline|Many members report feeling a difference within their first 1–2 sessions. Meaningful, lasting change typically develops over 2–6 weeks depending on how long misalignment patterns have been present.;Can I use my HSA or FSA account?|HSA / FSA Eligible|Yes. The Posture Guy Mike membership is one of the only posture programs that qualifies for HSA and FSA reimbursement. This means the membership may cost you nothing out of pocket.;What if it doesn't work for me?|30-Day Guarantee|Every membership includes a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you're not seeing results and you've put in the work, contact support and you'll receive a full refund — no questions asked." | split: ";" -%}

