        <p class="pgm-ap-faq__a">Yoga and stretching address flexibility and mobility, but they don't systematically correct structural misalignment. Physical therapy typically targets a specific injury site. The Egoscue Method maps your entire postural system and corrects the root cause — not just the symptom.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="pgm-ap-faq__item">
